biography: Janne, a familiar face at the Hector Trophée, is set to grace the greens once again at the upcoming Hector Trophée 2025, marking their seventh appearance in this esteemed tournament. Representing Revontuli Golf, Janne is known for their meticulous approach to the game and unwavering determination.

While the coveted Hector Trophée and the individual Victor Trophy have eluded them thus far, Janne's commitment to the sport and their strategic prowess make them a formidable competitor. Those who have the fortune of knowing Janne personally describe them as an extremely disciplined person who hates to be late, even if it's just by a single minute.
